TY  - JOUR
TI  - Some Tests of Dynamic Specification for a Single Equation
AU  - Sargan, J. D.
AB  - [This paper discusses the constraints on a dynamic equation represented by the possibility of factoring out an autoregressive error specification from a general lag structure. A suitable Wald test is defined and applied to a practical case.]
